Package org.apache.arrow.driver.jdbc.accessor.impl.numeric

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrowFlightJdbcBaseIntVectorAccessor
    Accessor for the arrow types: TinyIntVector, SmallIntVector, IntVector, BigIntVector, UInt1Vector, UInt2Vector, UInt4Vector and UInt8Vector.
    ArrowFlightJdbcBitVectorAccessor
    Accessor for the arrow BitVector.
    ArrowFlightJdbcDecimalVectorAccessor
    Accessor for DecimalVector and Decimal256Vector.
    ArrowFlightJdbcFloat4VectorAccessor
    Accessor for the Float4Vector.
    ArrowFlightJdbcFloat8VectorAccessor
    Accessor for the Float8Vector.
